hopobject.body: Could you ask him to call me? toprol xl goodrx However, it was an alert from a credit reference agency that made you aware that one month's payment had not been paid on the account. You then telephoned Vodafone to advise that the direct debit had been cancelled. You say you then gave your change of address details. Vodafone disputes this, saying you only gave these details later. As it only keeps records of such phone calls for 60 days it is impossible now to establish what was said or not.
